snippet.title: Butterscotch Party Mix
snippet.description: Butterscotch Party Mix is a great new twist on party mixes, combining sweet butterscotch and chewy caramel with nuts, pretzels and cereal.

snippet.title: Butterfinger Brownies
snippet.description: These brownies are made extra-special by adding chopped Butterfinger.

snippet.title: Original NESTLÉ® TOLL HOUSE® Chocolate Chip Cookies
snippet.description: This famous classic American cookie is a treat no matter what the age or occasion. Enjoy it with a glass of cold milk.

snippet.title: Ice Cream Sundae NESTLÉ® TOLL HOUSE® Cookies
snippet.description: Try this fun new idea for your next batch of chocolate chip cookies – simply add premier white morsels, broken sugar cone pieces and maraschino cherries to create an ice cream sundae-inspired cookie. Everyone will love this new flavor combination!

snippet.title: Deluxe Oatmeal Raisinets Cookies
snippet.description: Chocolate-covered raisins make these Deluxe Oatmeal Raisinets Cookies an unbeatable treat. Perfect for all occasions.

snippet.title: Tortellini Spinach Soup
snippet.description: Tortellini Spinach Soup is quick and easy and an excellent choice for a light lunch, dinner or first course!

snippet.title: Choco-Holic Cake
snippet.description: Chocolate, chocolate, chocolate is what this cake is made of! Sour cream and pudding mix enrich and make this cake moist and delicious.

snippet.title: Flourless Chocolate Brownies
snippet.description: Rich, decadent and oh-so-good, these moist chocolate flourless brownies topped with a layer of ganache will serve as the perfect treat after any meal.

snippet.title: Roasted Asparagus with Pesto & Lemon
snippet.description: Delicious Roasted Asparagus with Pesto & Lemon is ready in less than 30 minutes and is a perfect side dish for most any meal. It is bursting with flavors. Add shredded parmesan cheese for an elegant and tasty final touch.

snippet.title: Baked Ravioli in Alfredo Sauce
snippet.description: This hearty, flavorful Baked Ravioli in Alfredo Sauce dish will please everyone in your family.
